UK BEAM Trial Team.

Comment in
    BMJ. 2005 Jan 8;330(7482):53-4.
    BMJ. 2005 Mar 19;330(7492):674; author reply 674.
    BMJ. 2005 Mar 19;330(7492):674; author reply 674.

OBJECTIVE: To assess the cost effectiveness of adding spinal manipulation, 
exercise classes, or manipulation followed by exercise ("combined treatment") to 
